@tonyrobbins 2023 Platinum Partner Adventure Trip to Zambia, Africa! 🙌
.
.
.
#adventures #tonyrobbins #tonyrobbinsplatinumpartners #love #family #africa #zambia #fearless #courage

That time we went whitewater rafting down the Zambezi River in Africa… 😮
.
.
.
#africa #tonyrobbins #tonyrobbinsplatinumpartner #fear #zambia #whitewater #courage #wakawaka

I will never forget the beautiful people of Africa and Mukuni Village. @thetonyrobbinsfoundation installed a new water and plumbing system for the Mukuni Primary School, allowing for 24/7 water - a big change from the former 1 hour of water per day. They also donated $75,000 in goods and services to help this village.
My cofounded nonprofit, @unbreakable.threads with the help of amazing people from the @tonyrobbins #tonyrobbinsplatinumpartners donated 250 soccer jerseys, 30+ soccer balls, and committed $100,000 of goods and services to the school and village as well.
My heart is full. This was such a powerful place to learn what the human spirit is capable of, to fall in love with people on such a deep level, and to truly see that the secret to living is giving. I’m forever grateful! 💕
.
